Adam Ole Pedersen.

703
01:26:18,446 --> 01:26:20,846
We've been looking forward
to meeting you.

704
01:26:22,407 --> 01:26:25,583
Well, let's go.
I'll take the bags.

705
01:26:25,624 --> 01:26:28,024
What the fuck
is wrong with your eye?

706
01:26:31,322 --> 01:26:34,257
- What do you mean?
- You look like a retard.

707
01:26:35,383 --> 01:26:36,343
Really?

708
01:26:36,913 --> 01:26:39,313
I think that's an awfully
rude way to break the ice.

709
01:26:39,618 --> 01:26:43,890
We can go through town
and ask what they think of me.

710
01:26:44,579 --> 01:26:49,672
This is not the place for that
discussion because you'll lose.

711
01:26:52,634 --> 01:26:55,387
The eye is fine.
We'll discuss it in the car.

712
01:26:56,133 --> 01:27:00,371
Good idea there.
Come on.

713
